    "source": "EUMETSAT (2023): AVHRR Fundamental Data Record - Release 1 - Multimission, European Organisation for the Exploitation of Meteorological Satellites, DOI: 10.15770/EUM_SEC_CLM_0060. http://doi.org/10.15770/EUM_SEC_CLM_0060; DOI 10.15770/EUM_SEC_CLM_0060\u201d. Cloud mask is provided by CMSAF; This data is a non-operational, non-committed product of the CLARA-A3 climate data record (DOI:10.5676/EUM_SAF_CM/CLARA_AVHRR/V003) generated by EUMETSAT CM SAF. For terms of use see https://www.cmsaf.eu/intermediateLicence.",
